title: Top Places to visit in Ganderbal, Jammu and Kashmir
content: Ganderbal is a town and a municipality committee in Ganderbal district in the Indian Union Territory of Jammu and Kashmir. It has an average elevation of 1,619 metres (5,312 feet).
